.section *refid='cgraphic' cgraphic
.*
.ix 'cgraphic'
.ix 'Figures' 'character'
.tag begin
.tdesc
Creates a "text graphic." Any text in the cgraphic block will be rendered mono-spaced, and spaces and new-lines
will be honored. If the text does not fit within the window, it will be clipped. Although in-line formatting
is allowed, mixing bold and normal fonts will throw the spacing off.
.tclose ecgraphic
.tclass Block
.tcont Text, Formatting, In-line
.tseealso
:HDREF refid='artwork'., :HDREF refid='fig'., :HDREF refid='lines'.
.tag end

